In this video, we're going
to be taking a look at all

00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:06.400
of the different suggested methods
for making ice that is completely clear.

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:09.180
There are several of them,
and some will work, and some won't.

00:00:09.180 --> 00:00:10.320
We'll find out which.

