[Music]

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:17.740
Ice is really cool,

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:19.800
and of course, I mean
that in multiple ways.

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.200
But what's even better is if you can
have ice that's completely clear.

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:24.400
You can see right through it.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.700
But that's kind of
a hard effect to achieve.

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:29.700
Today, we're going to put
to the test several suggested methods

00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:31.940
for how to get clear ice.

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:34.300
The basic idea is we'll have
a separate container for each

00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:36.400
of our different methods
for making clear ice,

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:39.200
we'll let them all freeze,
