00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:43.212
This could be tricky.

00:08:46.432 --> 00:08:47.222
That sounded good.

00:08:48.372 --> 00:08:48.900
There we go.

00:08:48.900 --> 00:08:49.722
There's our block.

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:51.700
Oh boy.

00:08:51.700 --> 00:08:52.420
That's--

00:08:52.420 --> 00:08:53.600
That's fantastic.

